name: 突击队
description: 只是你那平平无奇的、充斥着人渣和恶棍的无底深渊。老板们争权夺利；契约被订立又被破坏；友谊在扭曲而微妙的匕首锋刃上结束。然而，这座城市还有更多的东西。一些未被发现、难以察觉的东西。一些……取之不尽的东西。

wikiSkinData.lore: Issues with the military industrial complex notwithstanding, why would a government put all its petricite resources into a giant statue that punches things? Or a pair of sunglasses big enough for one to wear?
An expert at jungle warfare, Xin Zhao can harpoon a fruit from the rainforest canopy at a hundred yards. He just chooses not to, because it gets fruit chunks all over his spear.

skins.name: 游击队员 崔丝塔娜

wikiSkinData.lore: The beauty of guerilla warfare is attacking an enemy that has their guard down, is unfamiliar with the terrain, and doesn't know who—or what—is engaging them. The beauty of being a two foot tall Yordle with a cannon the size of a mastiff hound is that no enemy would ever understand what hit them anyway.
How special are the special forces? Let's put it this way: they're the only unit in the military with unlimited access to oranges.

skins.name: 孤胆英豪 嘉文四世

wikiSkinData.lore: Yes, those are guns strapped to Jarvan's arms and legs. No, he can't shoot them.
Most commandos excel at amphibious attacks and military paragliding. This one spins very fast toward things while holding a giant sword. It's basically the same.
Soundproof ear protectors, a multispectral heat visor, lace-up knee-high boots, and a double-sided flamethrower that shoots lasers instead of fire? Lux really does have it all.
